### Produtos API — Requisições HTTP
### Porta: 8086

### ============================================================
### Listar todos os produtos
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Buscar produto por ID
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Buscar produto por SKU
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/sku/NTB-001
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Buscar por nome
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/search?name=notebook
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Buscar por faixa de preço
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/price-range?min=100&max=500
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Listar produtos em estoque (paginado)
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/in-stock?page=0&size=3&sort=name
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Criar produto
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8086/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Webcam HD",
  "sku": "WBC-006",
  "price": 259.90,
  "quantity": 20
}

### ============================================================
### Criar produto — Validação (nome vazio)
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8086/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "sku": "ERR-001",
  "price": 100.00,
  "quantity": 5
}

### ============================================================
### Criar produto — SKU duplicado
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:8086/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Outro Notebook",
  "sku": "NTB-001",
  "price": 3999.90,
  "quantity": 5
}

### ============================================================
### Atualizar produto
### ============================================================
PUT http://localhost:8086/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Notebook Dell Atualizado",
  "sku": "NTB-001",
  "price": 4999.90,
  "quantity": 8
}

### ============================================================
### Deletar produto
### ============================================================
DELETE http://localhost:8086/api/products/5

### ============================================================
### Buscar produto inexistente (404)
### ============================================================
GET http://localhost:8086/api/products/999
Accept: application/json
